My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 1

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014!

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle! It's NSW cheesemakers Annie and Jason's turn to cook. Will their paddock to plate philosophy shine through or will their kitchen bickering fan the flames in a tense showdown?
